235
00:08:51,661 --> 00:08:54,662
All right, so we had our diagrams and our staging ready,

236
00:08:54,662 --> 00:08:56,683
but how do we actually create the previs?

237
00:08:57,865 --> 00:09:01,388
Well, animators might recognize this sort of thing.

238
00:09:01,388 --> 00:09:04,170
