451
00:18:14,793 --> 00:18:17,495
it was very important to give our characters things to do,

452
00:18:17,495 --> 00:18:20,077
because this gave us opportunities for the camera

453
00:18:20,077 --> 00:18:21,859
to look away from the characters.

454
00:18:21,859 --> 00:18:23,139
