00:18:23,139 --> 00:18:25,301
but having something for the camera to look at

456
00:18:25,301 --> 00:18:27,443
and motivate to look away from the character's face

457
00:18:27,443 --> 00:18:28,183
was important.

458
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:31,942
Business would also provide motivation

459
00:18:31,942 --> 00:18:33,843
for getting the characters to move through the space.

460
00:18:33,843 --> 00:18:34,843
And if you think back to our early tests

461
00:18:34,843 --> 00:18:36,364
where the characters were kind of freezing

462
00:18:36,364 --> 00:18:37,745
