00:39:46,704 --> 00:39:48,706
Let's go into that debugging tool,

963
00:39:48,706 --> 00:39:50,628
and you'll see that at some point,

964
00:39:50,628 --> 00:39:53,350
the log's zero joint stopped moving,

965
00:39:53,350 --> 00:39:55,332
so it thought that it should not be moving forward,

966
00:39:55,332 --> 00:39:57,133
while Kratos kept walking along.

