sometimes there were clock physics problems

982
00:40:43,781 --> 00:40:45,442
because it thought the character was somewhere else.

983
00:40:45,442 --> 00:40:48,985
So you would see his skirt would flip out there.

984
00:40:48,985 --> 00:40:49,526
And again, pose mismatches.

