989
00:41:04,097 --> 00:41:06,179
and we haven't quite aligned them to the ground plane.

990
00:41:06,179 --> 00:41:07,600
So we're trying to figure out where that's going.

991
00:41:09,654 --> 00:41:13,315
Another big part of polishing our scenes were armor variants.

992
00:41:13,315 --> 00:41:15,316
Kratos has many armors.

