00:41:15,316 --> 00:41:18,757
And again, because we can't cut, we can't hide any armor swaps

994
00:41:18,757 --> 00:41:21,678
on a cut to get into our cinematics.

995
00:41:21,678 --> 00:41:25,219
Some problems with that were, of course, obstructing your face.

996
00:41:25,219 --> 00:41:26,820
We need to be able to see Kratos' face

997
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:30,221
during certain cinematics, but certain pauldrons

998
00:41:30,221 --> 00:41:31,742
would obstruct it, and that's troubling.

999
00:41:32,790 --> 00:41:35,711
Penetrations, we'd have stuff going into

1000
00:41:35,711 --> 00:41:38,013
other parts of the body, other parts of the armor.

1001
00:41:38,013 --> 00:41:39,333
This was a pretty extreme example.

1002
00:41:39,333 --> 00:41:41,635
