00:42:39,642 --> 00:42:41,422
and four different rope meshes,

1027
00:42:41,422 --> 00:42:43,683
and our animator placed them at different heights

1028
00:42:43,683 --> 00:42:45,104
to cover the range of variation

1029
00:42:45,104 --> 00:42:46,805
between our different shoulder pads.

1030
00:42:47,077 --> 00:42:49,618
then the integration team would script the visibility

1031
00:42:49,618 --> 00:42:51,719
on each of those rope meshes to turn on and off,

1032
00:42:51,719 --> 00:42:54,640
depending on what the player had equipped at the time.

1033
00:42:54,640 --> 00:42:54,700
Yes.

1034
00:42:54,700 --> 00:42:55,140
Why'd you say nothing?

